{"title_page": "Municipality of Zagorje ob Savi", "text_new": "{{short description|Municipality of Slovenia}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n<!-- See Template:Infobox settlement for additional fields and descriptions -->\n| name                    = Municipality of Zagorje ob Savi\n| official_name           =\n| native_name             = ''Ob\u010dina Zagorje ob Savi''\n| native_name_lang        = sl<!-- ISO 639-2 code e.g. \"fr\" for French. If more than one, use {{lang}} instead -->\n| settlement_type         = [[Municipalities of Slovenia|Municipality]]\n| image_skyline           = Izlake panorama.jpg\n| image_alt               =\n| image_caption           = \n| image_shield            = Zagorje ob Savi.png\n| shield_size             = 120x80px\n| nickname                =\n| motto                   =\n| image_map               = Obcine Slovenija 2006 Zagorje ob Savi.svg\n| map_alt                 =\n| map_caption             = Location of the Municipality of Zagorje ob Savi in Slovenia\n| pushpin_map             = \n| pushpin_label_position  = \n| pushpin_map_alt         =\n| pushpin_map_caption     = \n| coordinates             = {{coord|46|08|N|15|0|E|region:SI_type:adm1st|display=inline,title}}\n| coor_pinpoint           =\n| coordinates_footnotes   =\n| subdivision_type        = [[List of sovereign states|Country]]\n| subdivision_name        = {{flag|Slovenia}}\n| established_title       =\n| established_date        =\n| founder                 =\n| seat_type               = <!-- [[Capital (political)|Capital]] -->\n| seat                    =\n| government_footnotes    =\n| leader_party            =\n| leader_title            = Mayor\n| leader_name             = Matja\u017e \u0160vagan\n| unit_pref               = Metric\n| area_footnotes          =\n| total_type              =\n| area_total_km2          = 147.1\n| area_note               =\n| elevation_footnotes     =\n| elevation_m             = \n| population_footnotes    = <ref>[http://www.stat.si/popis2002/en/ Statistical Office of the Republic of Slovenia, census of 2002]</ref>\n| population_total        = 17067\n| population_as_of        = 2002\n| population_density_km2  = auto\n| population_demonym      =\n| population_note         =\n| timezone1               = [[Central European Time|CET]]\n| utc_offset1             = +01\n| timezone1_DST           = [[Central European Summer Time|CEST]]\n| utc_offset1_DST         = +02\n| postal_code_type        =\n| postal_code             =\n| area_code_type          =\n| area_code               =\n| iso_code                =\n| website                 = {{Official URL}}\n| footnotes               = Source: [[Statistical Office of the Republic of Slovenia]], census of 2002\n}}\nThe '''Municipality of Zagorje ob Savi''' ({{IPA-sl|za\u02c8\u0261o\u02d0\u027ej\u025b \u0254p \u02c8sa\u02d0\u028bi|pron}}; {{lang-sl|Ob\u010dina Zagorje ob Savi}}) is a [[Municipalities of Slovenia|municipality]] in central [[Slovenia]]. The seat of the municipality is the town of [[Zagorje ob Savi]]. Traditionally the area was part of the [[Upper Carniola]] region. The entire municipality is now included in the [[Central Sava Statistical Region]]. The population of the municipality is about 17,000.<ref>[http://www.zagorje.si Zagorje ob Savi municipal site]</ref> \n\n[[Archaeological record|Archaeological evidence]] shows that the area was already settled in the [[Bronze Age|Late Bronze Age]] and [[Iron Age]].<ref>[http://rkd.situla.org/ Slovenian Ministry of Culture register of national heritage] reference number e\u0161d 14622 & 14623</ref>\n\n==Settlements==\nIn addition to the namesake town, the municipality also includes the following settlements:\n{{Div col|colwidth=14em}}\n* [[Blodnik]]\n* [[Borje, Zagorje ob Savi|Borje]]\n* [[Borje pri Mlin\u0161ah]]\n* [[Borovak pri Podkumu]]\n* [[Brezje, Zagorje ob Savi|Brezje]]\n* [[Breznik, Zagorje ob Savi|Breznik]]\n* [[Bri\u0161e, Zagorje ob Savi|Bri\u0161e]]\n* [[\u010cem\u0161enik]]\n* [[\u010colni\u0161\u010de]]\n* [[Dobrljevo]]\n* [[Dolenja Vas, Zagorje ob Savi|Dolenja Vas]]\n* [[Dolgo Brdo pri Mlin\u0161ah]]\n* [[Dru\u017eina, Zagorje ob Savi|Dru\u017eina]]\n* [[Gol\u010de]]\n* [[Gorenja Vas, Zagorje ob Savi|Gorenja Vas]]\n* [[Hrastnik pri Trojanah]]\n* [[Izlake]]\n* [[Jablana, Zagorje ob Savi|Jablana]]\n* [[Jar\u0161e, Zagorje ob Savi|Jar\u0161e]]\n* [[Jelenk]]\n* [[Jel\u0161evica]]\n* [[Jesenovo]]\n* [[Kal, Zagorje ob Savi|Kal]]\n* [[Kandr\u0161e, Zagorje ob Savi|Kandr\u0161e]]\n* [[Kisovec]]\n* [[Kolk, Zagorje ob Savi|Kolk]]\n* [[Kolovrat, Zagorje ob Savi|Kolovrat]]\n* [[Konj\u0161ica]]\n* [[Kostrevnica]]\n* [[Kotrede\u017e]]\n* [[Log pri Mlin\u0161ah]]\n* [[Loke pri Zagorju]]\n* [[Mali Kum]]\n* [[Medija]]\n* [[Mlin\u0161e]]\n* [[Mo\u0161enik, Zagorje ob Savi|Mo\u0161enik]]\n* [[Orehovica, Zagorje ob Savi|Orehovica]]\n* [[Osredek, Zagorje ob Savi|Osredek]]\n* [[Pade\u017e, Zagorje ob Savi|Pade\u017e]]\n* [[Podkraj pri Zagorju]]\n* [[Podkum]]\n* [[Podlipovica]]\n* [[Pol\u0161ina]]\n* [[Poto\u0161ka Vas]]\n* [[Po\u017earje]]\n* [[Prapre\u010de, Zagorje ob Savi|Prapre\u010de]]\n* [[Ravenska Vas]]\n* [[Ravne pri Mlin\u0161ah]]\n* [[Razbor pri \u010cem\u0161eniku]]\n* [[Razpotje]]\n* [[Rode\u017e]]\n* [[Rove, Zagorje ob Savi|Rove]]\n* [[Rovi\u0161\u010de, Zagorje ob Savi|Rovi\u0161\u010de]]\n* [[Rti\u010de]]\n* [[R\u017ei\u0161e]]\n* [[Selo pri Zagorju]]\n* [[\u0160emnik]]\n* [[Seno\u017eeti, Zagorje ob Savi|Seno\u017eeti]]\n* [[\u0160entgotard]]\n* [[\u0160entlambert]]\n* [[\u0160klendrovec]]\n* [[Sopota, Zagorje ob Savi|Sopota]]\n* [[\u0160pital]]\n* [[Spodnji \u0160emnik]]\n* [[Strahovlje]]\n* [[Tirna]]\n* [[Vidrga]]\n* [[Vine, Zagorje ob Savi|Vine]]\n* [[Vrh, Zagorje ob Savi|Vrh]]\n* [[Vrh pri Mlin\u0161ah]]\n* [[Vrhe, Zagorje ob Savi|Vrhe]]\n* [[Zabava, Zagorje ob Savi|Zabava]]\n* [[Zabreznik]]\n* [[Zavine]]\n* [[Zgornji Prhovec]]\n* [[Znojile, Zagorje ob Savi|Znojile]]\n* [[\u017dvarulje]]\n{{Div col end}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\