al with cup.svg|16px]] Qatari Championship, with [[El Jaish SC (volleyball)|El Jaish]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://volleyball.qa/en/police-bag-elusive-qva-league-crown-after-al-arabi-pip-el-jaish-in-five-sets/ |title=Police bag elusive QVA League crown after Al Arabi pip El Jaish in five sets |work=www.volleyball.qa |date=12 February 2017 |accessdate=21 April 2020}}</ref>\n** '''2018/2019''' [[File:Simple gold cup.svg|16px]] [[Polish Men's Volleyball SuperCup#Winners|Polish SuperCup]], with [[PGE Skra Be\u0142chat\u00f3w]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.plusliga.pl/scup/subid/36513/s/news/id/258.html |title=Mariusz Wlaz\u0142y: zrealizowali\u015bmy pierwszy cel |work=www.plusliga.pl |language=pl |date=24 October 2018 |accessdate=19 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n* '''National team'''\n** '''2011''' [[File:Bronze medal world centered-2.svg|16px]] [[2011 FIVB Volleyball Boys' U19 World Championship|FIVB U19 World Championship]]\n** '''2012''' [[File:Bronze medal with cup.svg|16px]] [[2012 FIVB Volleyball World League|FIVB World League]]\n** '''2013''' [[File:Bronze medal northamerica.svg|16px]] [[2013 Men's NORCECA Volleyball Championship|NORCECA Championship]]\n** '''2014''' [[File:Simple gold cup.svg|16px]] [[2014 Men's Pan-American Volleyball Cup|Pan-American Cup]]\n\n===Individually===\n* '''2014:''' [[2014 Men's Pan-American Volleyball Cup|Pan-American Cup]] \u2013 Best Blocker  \n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.plusliga.pl/players/id/30572 PlusLiga player profile]\n* [https://www.worldofvolley.com/wov-community/players/13975/david-rodriguez-fiel.html Player profile] at ''WorldofVolley.com''\n* [https://volleybox.net/david-fiel-p2018 Player profile] at ''volleybox.net''\n* [http://www.fivb.org/EN/volleyball/competitions/Youth/Men/2011/Teams.asp?Tourn=BY2011&Team=CUB 2011 FIVB U19 World Championship \u2013 Team Cuba]\n* [https://www.fivb.org/EN/volleyball/competitions/WorldLeague/2012/Teams.asp?Team=CUB 2012 FIVB World League \u2013 Team 